				<h2>A calendar with character</h2>
				<br/>
				<h3>Actually, Trevor is an intelligent time management assistant,<br/> designed to help you make the most out of your day.</h3>
				<p></p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>



<div id="core-features" class="container-fluid">
		<div class="row background-image connected">
			<div>
				<h1 class="dark-blue">Connected</h1>
				<p>Trevor syncs with lots of amazing apps, such as Todoist, Wunderlist, Trello, Evernote and Pocket, so you can schedule everything you do, in one simple place.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row background-image intuitive">
			<div>
				<h1 class="dark-blue">Intuitive</h1>
				<p>Trevor's interface is incredibly intuitive, allowing you to plan your day with just a few swipes. The more you use it, the smarter it gets.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row background-image intelligent">
			<div>
				<h1 class="dark-blue">Intelligent</h1>
				<p>In the end of the day, Trevor is like a personal assistant. He understands natural language. He learns about your lifestyle. He maintains your schedule. All so you can live a better day.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
</div>


